Class BookingManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • BookingManager

  • public class BookingManager
extends java.lang.Object
    BookingManager hold list of CustomerTransaction and Price system. It supports prepareForBooking, processBooking, calculates booking price, processPayment, modify a CustomerTransaction and checkSale, listTop5BySales.
